entries.s_15: Were you able to find the girl's location?
entries.s_16: No. The information in the administrator's computer reports her as still being in this pen.
entries.s_17: What are you going to do now?
entries.s_18: I have some codes to a computer that should have more recent data.
entries.s_20: I don't know. I was hoping you could tell me.
entries.s_21: I really don't know. If I had to guess though, I would say the security area at the end of the north hall would be a good place to check.
entries.s_28: Yes I am actually. A small Rodian girl by the name of Neeka Z'all.
entries.s_30: I know her. Her parents escaped recently and left her here.
entries.s_34: I have no idea. After her parents escaped she was removed from general population and put in a disciplinary cell.
entries.s_38: Lower levels. I think you might be able to find out by searching the administrator's desk terminal. You can find it in his office on this level.
entries.s_40: Thanks, I'll look around for it.
entries.s_42: I can't believe they left their child here.
entries.s_44: We're not supposed to talk to each other.
